sections.text:
50-1909.Failure to cooperate; effect.

Failure to cooperate with an investigation by the office may result in public disclosure of the failure to cooperate.

SourceLaws 2015, LB598, § 9;R.S.1943, (2021), § 47-909;Laws 2025, LB298, § 53.Effective Date: June 5, 2025
